titles.title: A resolution commending the Rochester, Minnesota A's American Legion baseball team for winning the 2003 National American Legion World Series.
A resolution commending the Rochester, Minnesota A's American Legion baseball team for winning the 2003 National American Legion World Series.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.
